{"nodes":[{"pos":[12,49],"content":"Compiler Error C2111 | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C2111 | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,37]}]},{"content":"Compiler Error C2111","pos":[618,638]},{"content":"'+' : pointer addition requires integral operand","pos":[639,687]},{"pos":[694,786],"content":"An attempt was made to add a nonintegral value to a pointer using the plus ( <ph id=\"ph1\">`+`</ph> ) operator.","source":"An attempt was made to add a nonintegral value to a pointer using the plus ( `+` ) operator."},{"content":"The following sample generates C2111:","pos":[793,830]}],"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Error C2111 | Microsoft Docs\"\nms.custom: \"\"\nms.date: \"11/04/2016\"\nms.reviewer: \"\"\nms.suite: \"\"\nms.technology: \n  - \"devlang-csharp\"\nms.tgt_pltfrm: \"\"\nms.topic: \"article\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"C2111\"\ndev_langs: \n  - \"C++\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"C2111\"\nms.assetid: 38fd42ec-1480-4a44-aaca-ae4593ed5f50\ncaps.latest.revision: 9\nauthor: \"corob-msft\"\nms.author: \"corob\"\nmanager: \"ghogen\"\ntranslation.priority.ht: \n  - \"de-de\"\n  - \"es-es\"\n  - \"fr-fr\"\n  - \"it-it\"\n  - \"ja-jp\"\n  - \"ko-kr\"\n  - \"ru-ru\"\n  - \"zh-cn\"\n  - \"zh-tw\"\ntranslation.priority.mt: \n  - \"cs-cz\"\n  - \"pl-pl\"\n  - \"pt-br\"\n  - \"tr-tr\"\n---\n# Compiler Error C2111\n'+' : pointer addition requires integral operand  \n  \n An attempt was made to add a nonintegral value to a pointer using the plus ( `+` ) operator.  \n  \n The following sample generates C2111:  \n  \n```  \n// C2111.cpp  \nint main() {  \n   int *a = 0, *pa = 0, b = 0;  \n   double d = 0.00;  \n  \n   a = pa + d;   // C2111  \n   a = pa + b;   // OK  \n}  \n```"}